Welcome to Your Prescribed Fire Smoke Impacts Q Sort!

This research project is part of an ongoing study at the University of Florida to learn about preferences for smoke impacts created from prescribed fires. This research is approved by the University of Florida Institutional Review Board(Protocol #: ET00047508). Your participation is voluntary. You can decide not to participate or later decide to stop participating at any time without penalty or lose any benefits that would normally be expected.{br}{br}{b}** Important Information **{/b}{br}For this survey you will need as much screen space as possible!{br}{br}If necessary, please {b}MAXIMIZE{/b} the size of your browser window, {b}{i}reload{/i}{/b} this web page, and click on the "Continue" button to start the survey.



